# Title: Renamed Plink Execution
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-06-06
# Level: high
# Description: Detects the execution of a renamed version of the Plink binary
# MITRE Tactic: Defense Evasion
# Tags: attack.defense-evasion, attack.t1036
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_renamed_plink.yml

OriginalFileName="Plink" OR (CommandLine="* -l forward*" CommandLine="* -P *" CommandLine="* -R *") NOT Image="*\\plink.exe"